WEBVTT

07:03.725 --> 07:11.348
Doctor Warren has clearly told you about these
subtle bodies within us.

07:12.374 --> 07:18.467
And we should think why this subtle body was
created?

07:19.396 --> 07:24.867
What was the need to create this body within us
and how it was created?

07:25.570 --> 07:33.465
These, all these centers, are the milestones
of our evolution.

07:33.465 --> 07:43.344
And as we started growing, higher and higher,
developing higher and higher awareness, we

07:43.686 --> 07:46.366
developed all these centers one by one.

07:46.366 --> 07:52.837
And at the human level, it’s this center
where the man raised his head up.

07:52.837 --> 07:54.126
Still why?

07:54.126 --> 07:58.517
What was the need to create a human being?

07:58.517 --> 08:04.217
Supposing I’m trying to get some nuts, bolts
and things, and try to fix them up,

08:04.413 --> 08:07.907
make it into a good instrument.

08:07.907 --> 08:10.167
One would ask what are you doing?

08:10.167 --> 08:13.027
Why are you assembling all this, what are
you making out of it?

08:13.027 --> 08:21.186
After all, it cannot be a waste, why such
a special thing has been made, for what purpose?

08:21.186 --> 08:26.237
And that is what we have not yet discovered,
what is our purpose.

08:26.237 --> 08:31.258
But if you go to any of the Scriptures, you’ll
find out that they have said,

08:31.258 --> 08:36.266
all of them have said, that you have to become your Self.

08:36.266 --> 08:41.167
That there is All-pervading Power around us.

08:41.167 --> 08:43.997
Now this All-pervading Power we cannot see.

08:43.997 --> 08:45.937
It exists.

08:45.937 --> 08:48.946
As they say, if you have to believe it, or
not.

08:48.946 --> 08:52.837
But we should find out if there is such a
Power or not.

08:52.837 --> 09:00.369
For example, if I say that there are lots of
beautiful pictures

09:00.369 --> 09:05.807
and beautiful music in this area, you won’t believe it.

09:05.807 --> 09:13.147
But if I get you a television set and if I
plug it to the main, you starts seeing

09:13.147 --> 09:16.717
that it is receiving something.

09:17.364 --> 09:24.349
In the same way, when you become connected
with the whole,

09:25.229 --> 09:31.547
then what should happen to you is that you start feeling that All-pervading Power.

09:31.547 --> 09:33.857
This is Self-knowledge.

09:35.176 --> 09:42.857
And it’s written at length, very clearly,
by many people in the Indian Scriptures.

09:42.857 --> 09:52.516
The reason was, the people who came in the
other parts of the world,

09:52.516 --> 10:00.398
had such a tough time, they were not given any chance to say
anything much about it.

10:00.398 --> 10:09.147
Hardly they could utter anything and they
were crucified, poisoned, beaten up, tortured,

10:09.147 --> 10:14.647
all kinds of problems they were given.

10:15.136 --> 10:21.761
So this has to happen within us that you we
should feel this All-pervading Power.

10:23.152 --> 10:27.297
The other day, we had 2 persons from a guru
and they said,

10:27.297 --> 10:32.544
"How can it be only this cool breeze that is coming in us, is something?"

10:32.544 --> 10:38.645
For a human being, to conceive something about
God,

10:38.645 --> 10:46.717
is to go to scriptures which have lasted for all these ages, to find out

10:47.010 --> 10:50.072
one of the authorities you can have.

10:50.461 --> 10:55.107
Now, it is said that there is All-pervading
power in all the scriptures.

10:56.465 --> 11:02.356
Now supposing, by going to somebody, he says,
"I give you power called, so called shaktipat",

11:02.356 --> 11:09.060
and he just starts jumping like a mad horse
or a like a mad monkey.

11:09.060 --> 11:12.357
And you say, "It is shaktipat!"

11:12.357 --> 11:17.712
And you have vigorous movements and all kinds
of acrobats you fall into

11:17.712 --> 11:19.787
and you believe that this is shakti.

11:19.787 --> 11:24.785
And then, by the time it is over, you are
exhausted and finished.

11:25.416 --> 11:27.976
How can that be a shaktipat?

11:29.149 --> 11:37.551
The idea of energy within us is not horse
energy by which a horse can run very fast,

11:37.551 --> 11:41.756
that’s physical energy, we should understand.
That's just a 'prana shakti',

11:42.245 --> 11:46.717
part of this- just part of this path.

11:46.717 --> 11:49.908
It’s just a physical energy.

11:51.587 --> 11:56.927
Now human beings don’t need a horse power,
do they?

11:56.927 --> 12:01.527
You have already got big cars here which have
tremendous horse powers.

12:01.527 --> 12:06.477
You don’t have to become horses now, or
bulls or some sort of an animal.

12:07.552 --> 12:11.846
Our idea of a Superman is that he will have
such power

12:11.846 --> 12:15.710
that he can lift the whole building and throw away somewhere.

12:15.710 --> 12:20.757
All such absurd ideas should be given up

12:20.757 --> 12:25.592
and you should understand that is physical wellbeing

12:25.967 --> 12:35.477
so that you can feel the blessings, the
blessings of your Spirit.

12:36.943 --> 12:44.856
Blessing work, an animal doesn’t understand;
but a human being must understand that when

12:44.856 --> 12:53.787
he gets spiritually endowed and spiritually
blessed, then, first thing he should have

12:53.787 --> 12:57.307
is a physical wellbeing.

12:57.307 --> 13:04.637
That doesn’t mean that he becomes a wrestler,
That doesn’t mean that his body will be

13:04.637 --> 13:10.636
so built that if he slaps somebody, then the
other person will die.

13:10.636 --> 13:18.227
On the contrary, you become such a powerful
personality that if somebody slaps him, for

13:18.227 --> 13:21.967
him it’s nothing, it is all nonsense.

13:21.967 --> 13:33.007
So the concept of human beings can be from
the kind of life they lead, the kind of media

13:33.007 --> 13:39.907
they face, the kind of identification the
society has, all kinds of things could be there.

13:39.907 --> 13:46.717
For example, for Japanese children, I was
amazed, for them the idea of a Superman is

13:46.717 --> 13:52.841
that he should look like a ghost, he should
at least ten times bigger than a normal human being.

13:52.841 --> 13:55.267
