It's possession on you.

14:30.310 --> 14:35.477
Anywhere you go anybody who’s possessed, you
go and see lunatics, they do the same.

14:35.477 --> 14:42.121
You pay these people to become lunatics, to
believe that they have given you a power,

14:42.437 --> 14:44.001
it’s absurd.

14:44.001 --> 14:51.115
Now the power that has come, is going to come
to us, has to give you a wellbeing.

14:51.115 --> 14:54.880
All these people if you look at them, they
are sickly people, they are reclusive.

14:54.880 --> 15:00.525
