15:11.652 --> 15:16.131
And that you should be able to feel this All-pervading Power that is there.

15:16.131 --> 15:21.236
This is Self-knowledge, this is 'atma bodha'.

15:22.126 --> 15:29.491
'Bodha' means to know; to know, to feel that
power.

