of your own Self

18:46.976 --> 18:50.735
as if you are going in the car

18:50.735 --> 18:56.717
and you get out of the car to see what’s
wrong with the car.

18:57.800 --> 19:02.190
It is very simple when the Kundalini rises
to correct you.

19:02.581 --> 19:05.879
For example, supposing there’s a person
who smokes too much.

19:06.717 --> 19:09.950
I may tell him, "Don’t smoke, don’t smoke", all that.

19:09.950 --> 19:14.345
He gets tired of me, run away, won’t see me again.

19:14.345 --> 19:17.124
