19:17.124 --> 19:20.847
Once you get your Self-realization, you won’t
smoke at all.

19:20.847 --> 19:24.796
Little willpower will work it out,  in the
first instance.

19:24.865 --> 19:31.282
But even if it doesn’t act in the first instance,
gradually you will just drop it out

19:31.282 --> 19:34.866
because of transmutation that takes place.

19:34.866 --> 19:40.622
So we have to see that when we say that we
have got some sort of a shakti or a power within us,

19:40.622 --> 19:52.191
we should become master of ourselves,
of our greed, of our desires and of our aggressive nature.

19:52.191 --> 19:54.923
We should become the master of that.

19:54.923 --> 19:59.612
Unless and until that happens to us, how should
we believe that it is innate power?

19:59.612 --> 20:03.845
and that we should feel this All-pervading, blissful
Power around us.

20:03.845 --> 20:08.162
Unless and until you’re awakened to that,
how can you see?

20:08.162 --> 20:12.677
Unless and until you eyes are open, how will
you see that?

20:12.677 --> 20:16.717
