and you must know that his power is flowing to you.

21:44.698 --> 21:50.724
That’s why one should understand what we
should expect when we get our Realization.

21:50.724 --> 21:55.569
Of course, as we said, that when you start
getting the power within you,

21:55.569 --> 22:02.373
