a car and they give you everything in writing,

22:28.426 --> 22:33.907
"Now try this one. If you press this button, that will
happen. If you  press that button, that will happen."

22:33.907 --> 22:37.877
In the same way, the whole thing is invented

22:37.877 --> 22:44.597
completely decorated for you to use this power

22:44.597 --> 22:52.678
to manoeuvre it, to handle it and to manifest it.

22:55.024 --> 23:03.409
