29:55.638 --> 30:00.073
and his Power that is the Primordial Power,

30:00.073 --> 30:06.717
in Sanskrit is called as Adi Shakti,
and we call it as Holy Ghost in the Bible.

30:07.157 --> 30:12.053
So, they separate, I mean it’s a –

30:12.053 --> 30:17.223
some drawings have to be made but doesn’t matter now- I'll just tell you in short.

30:17.223 --> 30:23.345
And this Spectator, this Sadashiva,

30:23.345 --> 30:28.997
this God Almighty starts watching his own Power.

30:28.997 --> 30:36.046
Now we cannot understand the complete concord and complete understanding,

30:36.046 --> 30:42.096
complete oneness and integration between these two entities,

30:42.096 --> 30:48.859
God Almighty and his Power. It’s like the Sun and his rays or sunshine,

30:48.859 --> 30:53.294
Moon and moonlight, but even more than that.

30:53.294 --> 30:55.439
Nothing can come in between them.

30:55.439 --> 31:01.001
They are absolutely in unison with each other

31:01.001 --> 31:05.302
and every thing works simultaneously.

31:05.302 --> 31:12.496
