31:31.348 --> 31:38.061
And then He gives Her- I mean in a very poetic way- it’s called as a “Lasya”, means a launch.

31:38.061 --> 31:42.052
And that gives the first sound, Omkara.

31:42.052 --> 31:46.717
That’s the first, logos, the first sound, the Word.

31:46.717 --> 31:52.625
That’s the Word She says, She creates.

31:53.114 --> 31:56.717
Then She starts creating.

31:56.717 --> 31:59.065
She creates, She divides Herself

31:59.065 --> 32:03.684
First of all, She is nothing but the Power of desire.

32:03.684 --> 32:11.292
Because, first it is to be desired! It’s the God’s desire!

32:11.292 --> 32:13.765
She exists as a desire.

32:13.765 --> 32:17.548
Unless and until there is desire, nothing can work out.

32:17.548 --> 32:23.909
So She is the Power of desire. like we have also the Power of desire within us.

32:23.909 --> 32:33.628
Then from this desire, comes the other Power which makes it an act.

32:33.628 --> 32:39.396
So the other Power of action comes in.

32:39.836 --> 32:50.019
These two Powers bring forth a system in between themselves,

32:50.019 --> 32:53.570
like left and right,

32:53.570 --> 32:58.182
which starts giving sustenance to things that have been created.

32:58.573 --> 33:04.760
As I told you that carbon has four valences, it’s a tetravalent,

33:04.760 --> 33:10.646
I don’t know if you people have studied chemistry or not, there’s a chemical periodic table if you see,

33:10.646 --> 33:15.764
it’s all divided so beautifully and it is so well arranged,

33:15.764 --> 33:21.388
that one has to believe that there is a great Juggler

33:21.388 --> 33:26.300
or a great Planner who has done it, otherwise it’s not possible.

33:26.300 --> 33:32.043
It’s so well arranged! The whole valences system and everything is so well arranged.

33:32.043 --> 33:43.945
All this is done by the central path which gives them the sustenance, the quality that they have.

33:43.945 --> 33:47.176
Then the sustenance starts growing

33:47.176 --> 33:51.651
till you become a human being as shown here.

33:51.651 --> 33:57.978
In this Void, here as carbon then you move into the Void

33:57.978 --> 34:04.172
and here you go through all the evolution starting from a fish

34:04.172 --> 34:09.341
up to the human level where you become a small man.

34:09.732 --> 34:15.811
Once you become the small man, Vamana, is called that.

34:15.811 --> 34:21.172
First the man who came on this earth was a small statured man.

34:21.563 --> 34:31.259
Then a man came who was Parashurama, a very, very - Poseidon, a very large man, huge man.

34:31.845 --> 34:34.809
Two extremes.

34:34.809 --> 34:41.207
And then, came the man who was in the centre.

34:41.207 --> 34:49.285
And the leadership of all this evolution was done by the Incarnation

34:49.285 --> 34:54.136
of the aspect which is the evolutionary aspect.

34:54.136 --> 34:59.549
So the first aspect She creates is of desire aspect.

34:59.549 --> 35:04.251
When the desire dies, the whole thing is destroyed.

35:04.251 --> 35:06.913
And the Spectator is watching it.

35:06.913 --> 35:09.134
Spectator has a desire.

35:09.134 --> 35:13.257
As long as the Spectator is happy, the play goes on.

35:13.257 --> 35:17.973
As soon as He doesn’t like the spectacle, He disappears.

35:17.973 --> 35:29.172
As soon as He disappears, then the whole show is over.

35:29.172 --> 35:34.408
It’s for that only Spectator the whole show is there.

35:34.408 --> 35:39.784
So this Power of desire has to be till the end.

35:39.784 --> 35:44.022
Once the Power of desire is finished, then there is no more show;

35:44.022 --> 35:46.718
there’s no more Spectator,

35:46.718 --> 35:49.670
there’s no more his Power, they’re all merge together

35:49.670 --> 35:53.111
and again become the Parabrahma status.

35:55.263 --> 35:57.906
Now the other Power, as I said,

35:57.906 --> 36:01.814
which is the aspect of creation so the Creator aspect is there.

36:01.814 --> 36:08.415
One is the one which is the existence and the other side of the existence is the Destroyer.

36:08.415 --> 36:11.928
And then another aspect is of the Creator

36:11.928 --> 36:18.386
and the central one is the Sustainer, is the Protector.

36:18.386 --> 36:26.200
Out of these, this one incarnates, only one aspect

36:26.200 --> 36:30.997
because it has to give a quality and the leadership.

36:30.997 --> 36:35.128
For example, when there was a great flood,

36:35.128 --> 36:38.049
then He [Vishnu] incarnated.

36:38.049 --> 36:41.189
He incarnated as a fish

36:41.189 --> 36:44.949
and the dolphin-fish. Dolphin.

36:44.949 --> 36:48.609
I don’t know if you know about dolphins or not.

36:48.609 --> 36:52.893
But dolphin is a mammal and is a friend of human beings.

36:52.893 --> 36:58.721
So He incarnated as a dolphin-fish and saved the boat [Noa’s Ark].

36:58.721 --> 37:03.711
As you know, there was a boat in which people were saved.

37:03.711 --> 37:09.283
He saved the boat. He is the dolphin who incarnated on this Earth.

37:09.625 --> 37:13.583
One by one, He incarnates.

37:13.583 --> 37:19.382
Then He incarnates as a turtle,

37:19.382 --> 37:24.235
four legged, which comes out of the water

37:24.235 --> 37:29.027
to show the fishes that you can come out.

37:31.027 --> 37:36.301
Then, gradually He incarnates as a quadruped.

37:36.301 --> 37:40.696
Like that, the Incarnations — He comes as a leader.

37:40.696 --> 37:45.531
Somebody has to give that confidence.

37:45.531 --> 37:50.268
One fish comes and takes them out

37:50.268 --> 37:54.281
and others come, they follow them up.

37:54.574 --> 38:00.802
As they go on improving, every time there is an Incarnation.

38:00.802 --> 38:05.069
And between one Incarnation and another Incarnation,

38:05.069 --> 38:10.240
there is a very great time

38:10.240 --> 38:15.431
and that is called as 'Yugas [eras].

38:16.017 --> 38:21.279
Like that, these Incarnations come on this Earth.

38:21.572 --> 38:27.881
Plus the incarnations of the Primordial Being come in this area [Void]

38:27.881 --> 38:32.126
- where we can say this is the Ocean of Illusions -

38:32.126 --> 38:35.818
and try to save the people

38:35.818 --> 38:43.189
from getting too much to that side [right] or to this side [left] as I told you yesterday.

38:44.411 --> 38:50.565
And that time, when they become human beings,

38:50.565 --> 38:55.556
then the seekers are born, which you are,

38:55.556 --> 39:03.070
which are the epitome, epitome of human evolution.

39:03.363 --> 39:12.662
Now these seekers are engulfed by forces of ignorance

39:12.662 --> 39:17.342
and these ignorance forces also form anti-Christ.

39:17.342 --> 39:25.598
They can be devilish because they think, “Why are we not there?” like a competition setting.

39:25.598 --> 39:31.755
And they try to retard the progress of the saints.

39:31.755 --> 39:37.427
That’s why a seeker, when he’s born, is attacked,

39:37.818 --> 39:44.121
from very childhood, immediately he is attacked.

39:44.121 --> 39:47.398
Even the parents may attack the seeker.

39:47.398 --> 39:49.588
They may act through the parents.

39:49.588 --> 39:54.238
If not the parents, then the society, the schools.

39:54.238 --> 39:56.717
They’re all the time attacked.

39:56.717 --> 40:05.185
The people who are attacking may not be aware of it but they are used as mediums and these people are attacked.

40:06.260 --> 40:12.596
And with that attack, when they are absolutely in a mess,

40:12.841 --> 40:17.255
and they don’t know how to save themselves,

40:17.499 --> 40:23.434
then, another Incarnation is specially made,

40:24.314 --> 40:29.488
is the One that manifest here

40:29.488 --> 40:39.079
who is the desire Power of God, but is the Destroyer part,

40:39.421 --> 40:49.441
who is born to destroy these evil forces, to kill them.

40:51.151 --> 41:03.023
This is 14 thousand years back, the first incarnation of this great Lady.

41:04.391 --> 41:10.888
She’s called as Jagadamba, the Mother of this world.

41:10.888 --> 41:16.717
She comes in there [centre heart]. She saves them.

41:16.717 --> 41:26.235
Today is the first day, we celebrated the first day of an Incarnation

41:26.235 --> 41:37.041
and that is a very, very important day for Indians, because they believe in Shakti and She is the Shakti,

41:37.041 --> 41:45.735
that she came on this earth to kill these horrible devilish incarnations

41:45.735 --> 41:50.678
who are called as rakshasas.

41:51.313 --> 41:57.368
So this part is represented within us

41:57.368 --> 42:07.540
at the heart level in the centre, in the vertical column

42:07.540 --> 42:14.373
and it manifests in the children till the age of 12 in the sternum

42:14.373 --> 42:20.894
and creates antibodies. She creates Her army as the antibodies.

42:20.894 --> 42:25.614
Till the age of 12 years the children develop those antibodies within themselves

42:25.614 --> 42:36.415
and whenever there is a danger, whether it is physical, emotional or spiritual danger,

42:36.415 --> 42:40.819
these antibodies fight.

42:40.819 --> 42:45.999
That’s why, when you are frightened, the sternum starts breathing fast

42:45.999 --> 42:58.205
and informs that all the antibodies should join hands to protect the subject.

42:58.596 --> 43:03.335
These antibodies are created here [centre heart].

43:03.335 --> 43:17.605
And the left hand side, left had side of this [left heart] is the essence of Motherhood.

43:17.947 --> 43:25.181
If in your childhood, your Mother had played a role

43:25.377 --> 43:34.760
which has given you fears or kind of a frightening experience, then this center goes out.

43:34.760 --> 43:38.476
We say the left heart is catching.

43:38.965 --> 43:43.670
Sometimes, if you are a bad mother also it might catch.

43:44.012 --> 43:50.033
The right heart is the one, is that of the father.

43:50.033 --> 43:57.696
And the fatherhood is expressed by the leader who came on this earth about 8 thousand years back,

43:57.696 --> 44:00.140
who is called as Shri Rama.

44:00.140 --> 44:04.052
He is not - if  you see here, He’s in the center.

44:04.052 --> 44:10.307
To make him a complete human being, He was pushed onto the right-hand side.

44:10.600 --> 44:13.044
He is Shri Rama.

44:13.044 --> 44:20.935
Shri Rama came on this earth to establish the institution of benevolent king.

44:21.717 --> 44:28.070
The political development and the political evolution started from his side.

44:28.070 --> 44:32.714
He is the one who gave leadership as a benevolent king,

44:32.714 --> 44:43.807
the one who represents God and who is a king. The idea of a king related to God came from Shri Rama.

44:43.807 --> 44:49.487
But the modern Kings are not like that, they have no relation with God.

44:49.487 --> 44:56.085
On the contrary, they are horrid people. Some of them are nothing but satanic people.

44:56.085 --> 44:58.774
Absolutely Satan they are!

44:58.774 --> 45:03.806
And you can see from the way they lead their lives and they have led their life before

45:03.806 --> 45:09.919
So the benevolence of Shri Rama is here to be followed

45:09.919 --> 45:17.469
by all the political leaders and all the people who are at the helm of affairs.

45:17.469 --> 45:21.943
He is the ideal that was created for human beings,

45:21.943 --> 45:29.454
to run their authority as the head,

45:29.454 --> 45:36.717
or the loving compassionate benevolent leader of the people,

45:36.717 --> 45:41.796
who has to govern them by making them respectful,

45:41.796 --> 45:45.070
by respect.

45:45.070 --> 45:54.748
And if human beings create such kings who are not respectable,

45:54.748 --> 46:00.230
those who have no human values, those who have no moral courage,

46:00.230 --> 46:04.576
those who are selfish, those who are self-centred,

46:04.726 --> 46:08.841
then they have nothing to do to be there.

46:09.525 --> 46:13.983
So this is the position of Rama who is the father.

46:13.983 --> 46:20.377
So the head of every state has to be the father of his subjects,

46:20.377 --> 46:28.392
that’s what He has tried to show by his life. So much so that He had to sacrifice his beloved Wife,

46:28.392 --> 46:31.814
whom He loved so much.

46:32.254 --> 46:37.596
But these days, you know, how people do for their own children, they’ll sell the whole country.

46:37.596 --> 46:40.525
In our India, they do it.

46:40.525 --> 46:47.323
Here it’s just the other way round, nobody cares for children at all and nobody knows whose children they are.

46:47.323 --> 46:55.318
But in India it’s the other way round, that they will even sell their country for their children.

46:55.318 --> 47:00.907
All these two extremes go against the character of Shri Rama.

47:01.836 --> 47:07.195
Now this is the character that was created 8 thousand years back.

47:07.195 --> 47:13.949
So I’ve explaining to you all these things.
Now this is the heart. In the heart resides the Spirit.

47:13.949 --> 47:20.853
The Spirit is watching the game of this creation,

47:21.391 --> 47:30.456
and is watching what is happening to this person, this person, to this person, to this person.

47:30.456 --> 47:37.091
Every body has got in their heart the Spirit

47:37.091 --> 47:40.979
which is watching.
It’s called as the “cetana” [consciousness],

47:40.979 --> 47:44.229
means the one, the knower of the field.

47:44.229 --> 47:51.874
So, he’s watching every minute; he knows what you do, when you go, what mistakes you create, he watching,

47:51.874 --> 47:54.819
he doesn’t interfere.

47:54.819 --> 47:59.364
He’s only- the interference comes from here [Swaddisthan?], from that thing,

47:59.364 --> 48:03.619
He tries to give you conscience, he tries to improve you.

48:03.619 --> 48:08.740
From here sometimes [Mooladhara], the wisdom part, he tries to tell you, “Be in the center”

48:08.740 --> 48:12.707
by punishing you and showing it is wrong.

48:12.707 --> 48:19.103
But he’s just watching the game, “Let’s see how far it goes.”

48:19.103 --> 48:23.165
He is 'the knower of your field'.

48:23.165 --> 48:27.291
He is the Universal Being within you.

48:27.291 --> 48:34.231
He is the reflection of that God Almighty who’s the Spectator within you.

48:34.671 --> 48:43.152
And his Power is this All-pervading Power which has created all this [the subtle system].

48:43.787 --> 48:50.692
So to feel this All-pervading Power, you have to become the Spirit.

48:50.692 --> 48:54.639
All this creation has no meaning if you do not become the Spirit.

48:54.639 --> 48:59.589
In the Vedas, the first, the very first stanza says that,

48:59.589 --> 49:03.193
"By reading Vedas, if you do not become Vedis [ wise men]

49:03.193 --> 49:07.472
-Vedinies- 'Veda' word comes from 'vidya'. Vidya means to know;

49:07.472 --> 49:12.492
if you don’t become the knowledge, then it has no meaning.

49:12.492 --> 49:21.838
But knowledge doesn’t lie in dancing and shouting and all the monkey tricks that people do;

49:22.132 --> 49:24.331
it’s no monkey tricks there.

49:24.673 --> 49:32.814
Knowledge is that you become the Self, you feel the All-pervading Power and by which you know everything else.

49:32.814 --> 49:39.316
That is Self-knowledge and that is what we have to achieve.

49:40.098 --> 49:47.296
If you do not want to become your Spirit,
I’m sorry, I’ve nothing to offer.

49:47.296 --> 49:53.637
If you have some other things in your mind, you can go away from here, but no use arguing it,

49:53.637 --> 50:00.430
there should be no argument about it.
If you don’t want to become, I have nothing to say,

50:00.430 --> 50:04.048
I’ve nothing else to offer or to request you.

50:04.048 --> 50:12.333
I would request you that you become your Spirit, then we’ll talk about it.

50:12.333 --> 50:17.220
And when you become your Spirit - there’s a very good book

50:17.220 --> 50:20.618
written by Adi Shankaracharya in the 6 century,

50:20.618 --> 50:24.797
the one who was the first Shankaracharya, nowadays all of them are horrible ones.

50:24.797 --> 50:30.952
One of them is now making a big umbrella of gold, set with diamonds, imagine!

50:30.952 --> 50:36.717
He’s a short fellow. I said,
"This umbrella will fall upon him one day".

50:36.717 --> 50:41.461
He’s trying to compete with Pope.

50:41.461 --> 50:45.860
And this Adi Shankaracharya has said that,

50:45.860 --> 50:53.703
"Nothing can work it out, no Yoge, no shankye, no. All these philosophies are useless.

50:53.703 --> 50:59.573
It only works out- no discipline, nothing-

50:59.573 --> 51:02.390
by the Grace of the Mother;

51:02.586 --> 51:09.228
by the Grace of the Mother who is the Kundalini herself, She’s the Primordial Kundalini.

51:09.228 --> 51:15.278
Only by the awakening of the Kundalini it works out. It’s clearly given but you people do not read those books.

51:15.620 --> 51:21.044
Today is the name of the Goddess. Ten of them are nothing but the different chakras,

51:21.044 --> 51:24.898
where She resides in the Mooladhara. She resides in the Swadhishthana.

51:24.898 --> 51:31.789
She resides in the Manipura, She resides in the - what you call - this Hridaya (heart) chakra.

51:31.789 --> 51:36.725
Then She resides in the Vishuddhi, then into Agnya, and then into Sahasrara.

51:37.311 --> 51:39.802
All these names are given there.

51:39.802 --> 51:45.649
Of course, it was not so clearly said as it is said today because the time was not there to say.

51:45.649 --> 51:50.661
But all these things are there: how she rises, how she breaks all these “granthis”

51:50.661 --> 51:55.034
which are between these two chakras, are the “granthis” means the knots.

51:55.034 --> 51:57.803
It’s so clearly given.

51:57.803 --> 52:01.112
It’s never given that you start jumping like a monkey,

52:01.112 --> 52:03.758
or you take out your clothes.

52:03.758 --> 52:08.455
All this nonsense is not there, on the contrary, it is said that this is all possession.

52:08.455 --> 52:14.323
You get “bhootagrasta”, means you get possessed by the dead.

52:14.616 --> 52:16.717
It’s so clearly given!

52:16.717 --> 52:25.708
But people don’t read these books: they jump onto people who have come here to show some sort of a mesmerism

52:25.708 --> 52:28.124
and accept it. But you are seekers.

52:28.124 --> 52:32.795
I would request you, you are seekers, first of all know that you are seekers

52:32.795 --> 52:37.340
and don’t be deluded by these false tricks.

52:37.340 --> 52:43.302
Do not waste your energy on these false things, you’ll become your Self.

52:43.302 --> 52:46.987
Of course, it goes without saying that

52:46.987 --> 52:52.460
the change, the transformation, comes in, in your awareness,

52:52.460 --> 52:56.663
first of all, in your awareness.

52:56.663 --> 53:03.639
Not in jumping and none of all these nonsensical things. I mean people think that if you become a stupid fellow,

53:03.639 --> 53:05.154
then your awareness has improved.

53:05.154 --> 53:10.285
Transformed, after all, after all you are transformed, you see, your were a sane person, you’ve become stupid.

53:10.285 --> 53:13.165
You are transformed in any case.

53:13.165 --> 53:19.250
If you become mad, then is it a greater transformation. Mother says, “All right, transformation. You have become mad!"

53:19.250 --> 53:25.677
You're sane people, you are landing in a lunatic asylum, you are transformed. And also transmutation has taken place.

53:25.677 --> 53:29.782
"Because now we wear dresses like lunatic people,

53:29.782 --> 53:32.745
we behave like lunatic people, transformation has taken place".

53:32.745 --> 53:38.099
It’s an ascent of the mind, you have to ascend.

53:38.099 --> 53:43.936
Your awareness has to ascend and not to descend. It’s very easy to descend.

53:43.936 --> 53:50.871
To move on to the left or to the right is not the way, but to move here into Super Consciousness.

53:51.311 --> 53:54.924
And that’s one thing one should know, should happen to you.

53:54.924 --> 53:59.736
That is the Self-knowledge. That is the thing one has to get

53:59.736 --> 54:06.961
is to awaken these centres within you which are represented on your fingers here,

54:06.961 --> 54:13.836
seven of these are shown here and then to feel the All-pervading Power to begin with.

54:13.836 --> 54:17.611
Once it has happened, then to know how to discern,

54:17.611 --> 54:22.544
how to decode, how to find out, how to improve, how to go further with it.

54:22.544 --> 54:25.224
First of all, get the connection!

54:25.224 --> 54:29.909
If your car has not yet started, what are you doing about it?

54:29.909 --> 54:37.447
It’s so simple and such a common sense, but I don’t know how these people have taken over it.

54:37.838 --> 54:44.774
The only problem, as I told you before, is this, that God has given you freedom.

54:45.165 --> 54:48.436
And that freedom is to be respected.

54:48.436 --> 54:54.015
But if you go to these people, you don’t ask any questions, you do as others are doing, just like monkeys.

54:54.015 --> 54:58.320
You don’t even think why they are doing it. I mean you see that it is so filthy!

54:58.320 --> 55:03.501
Like a gentleman who came to me, who went to a guru, and he was absolutely ruined.

55:03.501 --> 55:06.042
I said:  "How could you do it? You are an Indian.

55:06.042 --> 55:09.951
Don’t you know that this is not to be done?" He said, "I just tried to see.

55:09.951 --> 55:16.098
Just out of curiosity I went there. And then I also started jumping and I got into it".

55:16.489 --> 55:22.003
And for five years he was in it, he could not know that he was in it.

55:22.003 --> 55:26.380
I said, "For Indians they have some wisdom because they have read all these things, they know all about it.

55:26.380 --> 55:28.726
How could you do it?"

55:29.068 --> 55:34.932
They know that unholiness is not the way to God.

55:34.932 --> 55:45.120
Now, some of them can give you also an explanation that all your- you are to be cleansed.

55:45.706 --> 55:50.466
And you pay for it as if you go to some a laundry here, you pay for it,

55:50.466 --> 55:55.360
you put yourself into it, go into some turnings and you become cleansed.

55:55.360 --> 55:57.760
You are to be cleansed.

55:57.760 --> 56:01.298
You must see their life pattern, you see, you must see how they live.

56:01.298 --> 56:04.835
The person who cannot even smell a flower how can he cleanse you?"

56:04.835 --> 56:10.755
He himself needs a lot of treatment.

56:10.755 --> 56:16.037
Flower he cannot smell, can you imagine a man like that who cannot smell a flower?

56:16.037 --> 56:19.369
I mean he’s a dumb personality I would say,

56:19.369 --> 56:25.335
the most beautiful thing that is produced is a flower, how is he going to feel the human flowers?

56:25.335 --> 56:28.318
How is he going to enjoy?

56:28.709 --> 56:35.551
A person who cannot take out his goggles from his eyes and can’t face people,

56:35.551 --> 56:40.141
how can you believe that such a man could be something holy?

56:40.141 --> 56:45.204
Any holy person doesn’t have this kind of eyes.

56:45.204 --> 56:53.023
One has to know that if the person doesn’t lead a holy life and parasites,

56:53.365 --> 57:00.092
greedy  people, asking for money and Roll Royce and things like that, how such people, you think they can be a guru?

57:00.092 --> 57:03.506
You have no self esteem I should say.

57:03.506 --> 57:06.717
They are absolutely devils.

57:06.717 --> 57:11.518
But the problem in this, for me, the problem is very, very different.

57:11.518 --> 57:17.742
Krishna has said, "Yada yada hi dharmasya glanir bhavati bharata…

57:18.280 --> 57:23.754
Paritranaya sadhunang vinashay cha dushkritam
…sambhabami yuge"

57:23.754 --> 57:30.978
He said that, "Whenever there is the degradation of the sustenance,

57:30.978 --> 57:40.575
then, to save the Saints and to kill the Satanics,

57:40.575 --> 57:47.270
I come on this earth and take a form."

57:47.563 --> 57:54.870
Now the problem is, all the Saints have got these Satanics in their heads. My problem is very complicated.

57:54.870 --> 58:00.589
I know they are Saints, I know there are the ones who are seekers and have been for ages,

58:00.589 --> 58:06.478
but they are impressed by the Satanics and the Satanics are ruling.

58:07.211 --> 58:14.665
So if any- if the question of killing, 'samarak', of Krishna  comes in, you see, even if they are killed

58:14.665 --> 58:18.231
they are in your brains, then how can you kill?

58:18.231 --> 58:25.509
They have to go out of your brain. The complicated structure today of the seekers is this,

58:25.509 --> 58:31.664
that in their brains they have got all the Satanics centred, they cannot get rid of it.

58:31.664 --> 58:33.701
They are so impressed!

58:33.701 --> 58:40.853
Yesterday, the fellow said, "But Mother, everything is good, there is nothing like evil." I said, "Really?"

58:40.853 --> 58:53.676
You can imagine To believe in such a thing

58:53.676 --> 58:56.318
Then why do you need discrimination? Go ahead.

58:56.318 --> 59:01.048
Whether you go to hell or to heaven what does it matter? If there is no evil,

59:01.048 --> 59:07.382
enjoy your Hell! Have a holiday!

59:08.115 --> 59:13.609
Christ has so many times said about the Satan.

59:13.609 --> 59:18.471
Not only but He said that the Satan tried to tempt Him.

59:18.471 --> 59:25.704
He has talked of Satan and still, how do you believe that there is no evil? I just can’t understand.

59:31.138 --> 59:36.572
There is not only evil but the darkness is so great

59:36.572 --> 59:43.010
that we are standing at a point so precariously placed,  very precarious placed

59:43.010 --> 59:51.171
that people are more impressed by evil than by good. See how many people we are. Just see for yourself.

59:51.660 --> 59:58.162
Here we are for reality, you cannot pay for anything, you get your Realization,

59:58.162 --> 01:00:01.015
50% people have got Realization here,

01:00:01.015 --> 01:00:04.418
but how many people there are? And they have no patience even to sit down

01:00:04.418 --> 01:00:09.639
but I’ve known people: "I’ve been with a guru for 8 years. He is in my heart".

01:00:09.639 --> 01:00:15.188
The heart is all catching and you’re fainting all the time with the guru being there.

01:00:15.432 --> 01:00:19.658
The very big problem which you should realize these are all saints.

01:00:19.903 --> 01:00:25.670
My only concern is to save them.

01:00:26.110 --> 01:00:33.624
There are very subtle methods of sabotising of destroying the work of God.

01:00:33.624 --> 01:00:41.150
And you should know, when you get your Realization, that you have to become strong pillars of God’s work

01:00:41.150 --> 01:00:51.750
and not indulging into frivolous, useless, cheep things. But get to it, learn it, master it. You’ll become your own master.

01:00:51.750 --> 01:00:56.638
These gurus who have no powers, nothing, they have become gurus and have minted so much money out of you

01:00:56.638 --> 01:01:01.445
and you are the people who are Realized souls and you are so quiet.

01:01:01.445 --> 01:01:07.750
You should shout at the top of houses and say that these are false people,

01:01:07.750 --> 01:01:15.268
these are fake people. Christ himself has said that there will be false and fake gurus.

01:01:15.268 --> 01:01:19.068
And then people said that, "Why are you talking against them?"

01:01:19.068 --> 01:01:24.689
He said, "The Satan is are not going to talk against himself, his house".

01:01:24.689 --> 01:01:28.403
He said it clearly.

01:01:28.892 --> 01:01:35.213
And when people tell me, "Mother, don’t talk against them". I say, I always tell them, "I’ll talk, not only talk,

01:01:35.213 --> 01:01:39.699
but where ever it is possible, I'll tell them definitely,

01:01:39.699 --> 01:01:46.717
I'll verily say that these are Satan whom I know now for ages, for thousands of years, I’ve known them,

01:01:46.717 --> 01:01:51.500
each one of them, all their tricks I know. I know what they do to you.

01:01:51.500 --> 01:01:57.132
And don’t listen to them that they are cleansing you. Let them cleanse themselves and repent

01:01:57.132 --> 01:02:01.812
so that they don’t go back into Hell permanently.

01:02:02.056 --> 01:02:09.327
So here, at this stage of the Mother, She’s terrific.

01:02:09.620 --> 01:02:17.931
She protects you. She has many antibodies.

01:02:17.931 --> 01:02:29.117
Actually, these antibodies were created at a particular time when it was said that there was a Satan who could not be killed

01:02:29.117 --> 01:02:34.969
by the quadruped and the people who have two legs like human beings.

01:02:35.799 --> 01:02:47.234
So She created a special type of  a – gnat, you call that gnat? A black thing, with six legs,

01:02:47.234 --> 01:02:53.508
and She killed him. And these antibodies are those with the six legs.

01:02:53.508 --> 01:02:56.258
And they worked it out.

01:02:56.258 --> 01:03:00.595
There are there and She’s the one who protects us.

01:03:01.328 --> 01:03:09.266
Now, coming to the gross level, when a lady is worried

01:03:09.266 --> 01:03:16.924
about her security, which is very common in America, because husbands, if they have flirts,

01:03:16.924 --> 01:03:23.326
if they have no time for their wives, and if all the time, they tell the wife that, "You may have to leave the house",

01:03:23.326 --> 01:03:29.004
they develop the fear in this area [heart centre].

01:03:29.004 --> 01:03:40.358
And the disease which is caused by that is breast cancer, which is very common in America, breast cancer.

01:03:41.092 --> 01:03:45.734
Breast cancer is caused to women who have a sense of insecurity.

01:03:45.734 --> 01:03:49.280
In Sahaja Yoga, you can cure breast cancer.

01:03:49.280 --> 01:03:54.508
It’s very easy to cure breast cancer in Sahaja Yoga.

01:03:54.801 --> 01:04:00.284
Now the combination of this and this gives you asthma.

01:04:00.284 --> 01:04:06.295
Among men who have asthma, they must look after their fatherhood.

01:04:06.637 --> 01:04:11.652
Their own father- supposing somebody’s father is dead

01:04:11.994 --> 01:04:17.287
without the knowledge of the man or the father can possess also.

01:04:17.287 --> 01:04:21.069
In that case, you get this kind of a thing.

01:04:21.069 --> 01:04:26.717
Surprisingly, recently in London, one doctor, I don’t know how,

01:04:26.717 --> 01:04:32.875
he experimented with a lady that was suffering from anorexia.

01:04:33.636 --> 01:04:39.208
Her father had died and she would not eat her food.

01:04:39.208 --> 01:04:44.435
And many of them are like that whose father has died, they suffer from anorexia.

01:04:44.435 --> 01:04:51.500
And he said, "All right, let us see about your father. Let us do some sort of a ceremony for him."

01:04:51.500 --> 01:04:55.585
And she started eating all right, it’s most surprising.

01:04:55.585 --> 01:04:58.307
It came in the paper that he did that.

01:04:58.307 --> 01:05:05.526
That is how you can cure such women who suffer from a deficiency of a fatherhood;

01:05:05.770 --> 01:05:13.468
or may be we can say, if the father possessed you, if the child is thinking of the father all the time,

01:05:13.468 --> 01:05:15.835
all these things can be cured in Sahaja Yoga,

01:05:15.835 --> 01:05:21.092
which, I’m sure, when you will go further in the studies of Sahaja Yoga,

01:05:21.092 --> 01:05:27.286
you will learn one by one, how to cure such people who have these diseases.

01:05:28.459 --> 01:05:36.156
Now, I think I’ll leave these three centres for tomorrow and I’ll try to cover it up.

01:05:36.156 --> 01:05:41.056
But this is the Spirit that is still watching.

01:05:41.300 --> 01:05:44.943
When the Kundalini –this is the seat of the Spirit -

01:05:44.943 --> 01:05:49.248
when the Kundalini rises and she touches that seat,

01:05:49.248 --> 01:05:56.717
immediately, you get connected to the Spirit.

01:05:56.717 --> 01:06:01.459
And the Spirit, which is this All-pervading Power

01:06:01.459 --> 01:06:08.633
starts flowing through your hands as well as you start feeling it outside.

01:06:09.024 --> 01:06:15.720
The Spectator, the Witness, who was outside our central nervous system,

01:06:15.720 --> 01:06:21.041
now comes into our central nervous system and we know everything about it.

01:06:21.041 --> 01:06:25.976
as we start using this power of Spirit.

01:06:25.976 --> 01:06:29.785
If you remember, Christ was touched by some woman who was sick,

01:06:29.785 --> 01:06:34.235
and He felt the power flew to her and this is the same thing.

01:06:34.235 --> 01:06:41.002
But Christ was different. He was All-pervading Power. He was Omkara,

01:06:41.002 --> 01:06:44.814
that’s why He could walk on the water.

01:06:44.814 --> 01:06:52.389
But about Christ and about Shri Krishna, I’ll tell you later on, tomorrow, if you don’t mind.
